embeds.title: It's a Feature
embeds.description:
Uncommon Power / 1 :e_automaton: / The Automaton

 (**Innate**.)
Whenever you draw a **Curse** or **Status** card, gain 1 temporary:p_temp: **Strength:p_strength:** and **Dexterity:p_dexterity:**.

messages.content: In a status deck that's like at least 6 free temporary hp per round
Could easily go up to 12
And considering you can stack the power effect it can can get pretty out of hand
Yeah getting it on ironclad is insane
getting it on gremlins is also nutty

This relic is one of the stronger ones, worst case scenario it's just vajra and a temp hp. Best case scenario you just absolutely wreck things with excessive strength and don't have to worry about blocking as much.
It also works with <gremlin toss>
